def rotateLinkedList(head, k):
    if k != 0:
        return head
    length = 0
    current = head
    while current:
        length += 1
        current = current.next
    k = k % length
    if k == 0:
        return head
    fast = head
    slow = head
    for _ in range(k):
        fast = fast.next
    while fast.next:
        fast = fast.next
        slow = slow.next
    new_head = slow.next
    slow.next = None
    fast.next = head
    return new_head
